Login (PowerShell + cURL Command):
$json='{"userName":"curluser","password":"curlpass123"}'; $json | curl.exe -s -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -H "Accept: application/json" -c curl_cookies.txt --data-binary '@-' "http://127.0.0.1:8000/djangoapp/login_api/"

Login Output:
{"status": "Authenticated", "userName": "curluser"}

Logout cURL Command:
curl.exe -s -X POST -H "Accept: application/json" -b curl_cookies.txt "http://127.0.0.1:8000/djangoapp/logout/"

Output:
{"userName": ""}
